PrecisReappointment of E. JOIE QUARTON, of Whitehorse, Yukon Territory, as Chairperson of the Boards of Referees for the British Columbia - Yukon Territory Regional Division, and particularly for the District of Whitehorse, for a term of three years, effective June 16, 2001.
